CustomField.description: We use this field to define our target market. We rank our target firms by number of lawyers, and assign a unique rank number to each firm. Our 2008 list consolidates the 2008 NLJ 250, The Lawyer's 2008 UK 100, and Canada's 2008 Lexpert 30, and customers.
